{"tid":407410,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"彭定康盼林鄭說服中央商民主非顛覆","createTime":"2017-09-20T11:50:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-20T11:50:16.000Z","uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"7bbeab8c7cf76c9012f04ef3718a08d60b505a5b","tid":407410,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-20T11:50:16.000Z","msg":"前港督彭定康期望行政長官林鄭月娥能說服北京，香港人爭取民主不是顛覆行為，不要視港人為製造麻煩的異見人士。 <br />\n<br />\n彭定康到香港民主促進會演講，被問到有何忠告給行政長官林鄭月娥。午餐會題目是「塑造更好的未來」，前立法會議員劉慧卿借題發揮，叫身兼英國上議院議員的彭定康盡點力。他又提到入獄的黃之鋒等學生領袖現時雖身處困苦，但已得到國際知名度，勉勵他們堅守民主和法治的信念。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/512988/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E5%BD%AD%E5%AE%9A%E5%BA%B7%E7%9B%BC%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E8%AA%AA%E6%9C%8D%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE%E5%95%86%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E9%9D%9E%E9%A1%9B%E8%A6%86\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F512988%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E5%25BD%25AD%25E5%25AE%259A%25E5%25BA%25B7%25E7%259B%25BC%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E8%25AA%25AA%25E6%259C%258D%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25AE%25E5%2595%2586%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E9%259D%259E%25E9%25A1%259B%25E8%25A6%2586&d=%2Fb725qUfKpa4Zp6WvmEJvhv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=54532574\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F512988%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F%25E5%25BD%25AD%25E5%25AE%259A%25E5%25BA%25B7%25E7%259B%25BC%25E6%259E%2597%25E9%2584%25AD%25E8%25AA%25AA%25E6%259C%258D%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%25A4%25AE%25E5%2595%2586%25E6%25B0%2591%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E9%259D%259E%25E9%25A1%259B%25E8%25A6%2586&h=13c9621b\" target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/512988/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/%E5%BD%AD%E5%AE%9A%E5%BA%B7%E7%9B%BC%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E8%AA%AA%E6%9C%8D%E4%B8%AD%E5%A4%AE%E5%95%86%E6%B0%91%E4%B8%BB%E9%9D%9E%E9%A1%9B%E8%A6%86</a>"}]}